Description:
  This generator creates the necessary files for a work that extends
  PagedMedia's Work models and behaviors.

Example:
  rails generate paged_media:work PagedType

  This will create:
    app/models/paged_type.rb
    app/actors/curation_concerns/paged_type_actor.rb
    app/controllers/curation_concerns/paged_types_controller.rb
    app/views/curation_concerns/paged_types/.keep
    spec/factories/paged_type_factory.rb
    spec/models/paged_type_spec.rb
    spec/actors/curation_concerns/paged_type_actor_spec.rb
    spec/controllers/curation_concerns/paged_types_controller_spec.rb

  This will also:
    register PagedType as a valid curation concern in:
      config/initializers/curation_concerns.rb
